			Profile
			
			Yue(Layla)YingwasborninHangzhou,Zhejiang,China.AftergraduatingHangzhouNo.2HighSchoolin2004,sheattendedtheUniversityofHongKong,whereshereceivedaB.A.inEconomicsandFinancein2008.ShewassubsequentlyadmittedtoTheUniversityofTexasatDallasinthefallof2008andgraduatedin2013withaPhDdegreeinFinance.Shetaughttwosemestersof&quot;FinancialMarketsandInstitutions&quot;attheUniversityofTexasatDallasand&nbsp;attendedseveralfinanceconferencesduringheryearsofstudy,includingtheFMA,theAFA,andtheCICF(ChinaInternationalConferenceinFinance)andpresentedherresearch.&nbsp;
